info.title: Final Resting Place
info.description:
What's more disturbing? The fact that the dog killed the squirrel, the fact that I posted it here? Or the fact that I even took this picture?

So, not only was my work day 12 hours, the second I sit down at home to relax I hear a ruckus outside and find this little gem when I get out there. I really wish he'd been dead when I arrived... the little guy looking at me and gasping for air was a bit disturbing (yeah, that coming from the guy who took the photo of the corpse).

And the blood isn't the squirrel's. Bear bit his lip during the attack. Dumb dog. We had to clean up his brother shortly after 'cause Bear bled all over him while they played...
